{"tid":634535,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【有對話截圖】賭波貼士網大小通吃　女學生數百元都呃","createTime":"2018-04-19T10:16:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T11:37:35.000Z","uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5a5433d2bc1529113135dcbaea86a135be1e22c5","tid":634535,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T10:16:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">由過去揚言「做人做狗自己決定」，到今日轉攻女網民「幫姊妹發達」</span>，社交平台賭波貼士網騙案，禁之不絕。本報再接到數宗投訴，事主損失由幾百至數千元不等。有個案事主自言，誤信貼士網聲稱「命中率」高達九成，轉帳「入會」後收到假料，投注未中過，要求退錢又不果，血本無歸。<br />\n<br />\n有事主稱，看到社交平台上有組織聲稱可以幫人賺錢，見平台上貼出不少「贏錢經驗」，遂查詢會費及每場貼士收費等。對方聲稱貼士準確率高達九成，若計劃不達標，可以退回費用；又強調戶口有齊姓名和地址等資料，絕不「走數」。事主信以為真，轉帳2500元加入「5日計劃」，之後連續幾天根據報料投注，一場也沒中過。到他要求退錢時，對方再沒回應。<br />\n<br />\n另有平台以女網民為主要目標，多則facebook帖文聲稱，可以幫到女士「7日袋走20萬」、「過闊太生活」、「日日買新手袋」等。有女學生稱曾查詢入會事宜，支付500元以為可以「玩一星期」，對方卻稱她只是付了500元本金，不是會費；如要收到「貼士」，最低消費一個月，須另加6000元。事主以「無錢玩住」為由要求退回本金，由上月中多番追討到上星期，忽然收到一場「貼士」並稱「500一場計劃已完結」，之後平台再無回訊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180419/s00001/a0d7f805e7ba46355637c3d8cb2d3884.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180419%2Fs00001%2Fa0d7f805e7ba46355637c3d8cb2d3884.jpg&h=40a61603&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource: 明報<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180419/s00001/1524124705345\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180419%2Fs00001%2F1524124705345&d=rbZgbMu5vZD4Wk65H5avArZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=325d7f44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180419%2Fs00001%2F1524124705345&h=7b61826f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180419/s00001/1524124705345</a>"},{"pid":"ec9bd8e02377654066ce8200cc78e2117ea700d0","tid":634535,"uid":6222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T10:21:38.000Z","msg":"弱智妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢老母生少個腦比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993f0e6aeac064b461fe603bed7c553dee8aa55e","tid":634535,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T10:45:31.000Z","msg":"2018年了,呢類招數可以用到幾多年?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fbc05a54c3fde36d52f318cf554eed6201e9256","tid":634535,"uid":141295,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T10:52:46.000Z","msg":"我呢輪都賺到夠喇, 真係好想比人賺下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e124710e2591ba3f7d0d6ee88cb6e0e3c4ece980","tid":634535,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T11:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/164628_3ed3d4eeb1ac51f379d473b3f96f4dd4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F164628_3ed3d4eeb1ac51f379d473b3f96f4dd4.png&h=c1baa559&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"223ed43a0c3120d9be2020abb05f53634b7620bc","tid":634535,"uid":150635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T11:37:35.000Z","msg":"大家好呀！又係我boss哥幫你5日賺30萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}